	<h2>Understanding Emergency Call Scenarios in Business</h2>
	<p>In today's fast-paced business environment, emergency calls can make or break customer relationships. Whether it's a medical emergency, urgent service request, or time-sensitive business issue, how your organization handles these critical moments defines your reputation and reliability.</p>

	<p><strong>AI phone agents have revolutionized emergency call handling</strong> by providing 24/7 availability, consistent responses, and immediate escalation protocols. This comprehensive guide explores how businesses can leverage AI technology to manage emergency situations effectively.</p>

	<h3>Types of Emergency Calls Your Business Faces</h3>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Medical Emergencies:</strong> Health-related urgent calls requiring immediate response</li>
		<li><strong>Service Outages:</strong> Critical system failures affecting operations</li>
		<li><strong>Security Incidents:</strong> Theft, break-ins, or safety concerns</li>
		<li><strong>Property Emergencies:</strong> Fires, floods, or structural damage</li>
